gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 128, Raptors 112
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeated the Raptors, 128-112. Damian Lillard recorded 37 points and a new season high 13 assists for the Bucks, while Malik Beasley added a season high 30 points and four rebounds in the victory. Scottie Barnes led the Raptors with 29 points, nine rebounds, and seven assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Bucks improve to 7-4 on the season, while the Raptors fall to 5-6.
